    "sample_texts": [
      "The primary endpoint was change in HbA1c from baseline to week 26.",
      "Patients were randomized 1:1 to receive closed-loop insulin delivery or standard care.",
      "Adverse events included hypoglycemia (12.3%), hyperglycemia (8.7%), and infusion site reactions.",
      "Kaplan-Meier analysis showed a significant difference in progression-free survival (HR 0.72, 95% CI 0.58-0.89, p=0.003).",
      "The MPC algorithm adjusted insulin infusion rates based on continuous glucose monitor readings every 5 minutes.",
      "Subgroup analysis revealed greater treatment effect in patients with baseline HbA1c > 8.5%.",
      "Pharmacokinetic parameters: Cmax 245 ng/mL, Tmax 2.1 h, AUC0-24 1840 ng·h/mL, t1/2 8.7 h.",
      "Inclusion criteria: age >=18, histologically confirmed diagnosis, ECOG 0-2, adequate organ function.",
      "The adaptive trial design used Bayesian response-adaptive randomization with a non-informative prior.",
      "Safety outcomes: grade 3-4 neutropenia (22%), febrile neutropenia (8%), thrombocytopenia (15%)."
